{"tid":2324432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE隊友私密照被出賣！網揪2證據抓到：子瑜學壞了","createTime":"2020-12-14T02:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T06:01:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"903d07f9d84ac2d358d1440ef38395b4476138da","tid":2324432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"南韓女團twice中的台灣成員周子瑜，靠著甜美仙氣的外表，去年還獲選美國電影網站TC Candler公布「2019全球女星最美臉蛋」排行榜奪得冠軍。而擁有好人緣的她，與團員每個人感情也都相當好，沒想到近日其中成員MOMO睡著的模樣被拍下來，竟是子瑜拍的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/12/2877046-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F12%2F2877046-PH.jpg&h=0ee24b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜近日領養兩隻流浪犬Kaya和Butter。（圖／翻攝自TWICEIG）<br />\n<br />\n近日TWICE官方曬出多張日籍成員MOMO睡著的照片，除了她之外，旁邊還有愛犬Boo，只見MOMO一手拿著手機，但卻已經呼呼大睡，不過留言卻是用中文寫下「累到睡著的Boo媽媽☺️」此外，除了Boo之外，還有兩隻狗狗，就是子瑜近日飼養的Kaya和Butter，讓網友笑喊偷拍成員的兇手似乎就是子瑜本人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/14/2933925-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F14%2F2933925-PH.jpg&h=66b45f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲MOMO直播完後，呼呼大睡模樣被子瑜偷拍下來。（圖／翻攝自TWICEIG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/09/2871296-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F09%2F2871296-PH.jpg&h=c74314f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後，粉絲笑得大喊「兩個人都好可愛啊！」事實上MOMO為這麼累原因也悄悄曝光，原來是早前她才跟子瑜一起開vlive直播，兩人不只一起跟狗狗開心玩樂，子瑜甚至還當起中文老師，教MOMO講「平井桃好可愛」粉絲久違聽到子瑜講中文，都直呼太想念了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CIvFszDFLPm/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCIvFszDFLPm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725PY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=18eed08d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCIvFszDFLPm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=ba8efc75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CIvFszDFLPm/?utm_source=ig_embed</a>"},{"pid":"5fc9d531256f85d656332c7a16c3a4fd250f636c","tid":2324432,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"幸福小狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac087a793572c17c9e421dcab0652e7621d38933","tid":2324432,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"見到希切老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09435ab7867e8797cc86e03f079706fbdb922c8e","tid":2324432,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"子瑜隻手太瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5804c89bfe069b3fe95973b173fbdc714cf938","tid":2324432,"uid":137569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"903d07f9d84ac2d358d1440ef38395b4476138da","tid":2324432,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"南韓女團twice中的台灣成員周子瑜，靠著甜美仙氣的外表，去年還獲選美國電影網站TC Candler公布「2019全球女星最美臉蛋」排行榜奪得冠軍。而擁有好人緣的她，與團員每個人感情也都相當好，沒想到近日其中成員MOMO睡著的模樣被拍下來，竟是子瑜拍的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/12/2877046-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F12%2F2877046-PH.jpg&h=0ee24b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜近日領養兩隻流浪犬Kaya和Butter。（圖／翻攝自TWICEIG）<br />\n<br />\n近日TWICE官方曬出多張日籍成員MOMO睡著的照片，除了她之外，旁邊還有愛犬Boo，只見MOMO一手拿著手機，但卻已經呼呼大睡，不過留言卻是用中文寫下「累到睡著的Boo媽媽☺️」此外，除了Boo之外，還有兩隻狗狗，就是子瑜近日飼養的Kaya和Butter，讓網友笑喊偷拍成員的兇手似乎就是子瑜本人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/14/2933925-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://